sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente (Frontend)
    participant ApiKey as ApiKeyFilter
    participant CORS as CORS Config
    participant Controller as Controllers
    participant Service as Services
    participant Repository as Repositories
    participant DB as MySQL DB

    Note over Client,DB: Flujo de Petición HTTP con Seguridad API Key

    Client->>ApiKey: HTTP Request (con header X-API-KEY)
    alt API Key Inválida o Ausente
        ApiKey-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    else API Key Válida
        ApiKey->>CORS: Validación CORS
        CORS->>Controller: Pasa al Controlador

        alt Alumno Flow (/alumno)
            Controller->>Controller: AlumnoController
            Controller->>Service: AlumnoService
            Service->>Repository: AlumnoRepository / CursoRepository
            Repository->>DB: CRUD / Consultas
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: DTOs
            Service-->>Controller: AlumnoCompletoDto / CursoDetalleResponseDto
            Controller-->>Client: JSON Response / PDF

        else Curso Flow (/curso)
            Controller->>Controller: CursoController
            Controller->>Service: CursoService
            Service->>Repository: CursoRepository
            Repository->>DB: Consultas paginadas / Deuda
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: Page<CursoDto> / DeudaCursoResponseDto
            Service-->>Controller: Datos estructurados
            Controller-->>Client: JSON / PDF

        else Factura Flow (/facturacion)
            Controller->>Controller: FacturaController
            Controller->>Service: FacturaService
            Service->>Repository: FacturaRepository / CuentaCorrienteRepository
            Repository->>DB: JOINs / Agregaciones
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: Reportes / Detalles
            Service-->>Controller: DTOs de Facturación / PDF
            Controller-->>Client: JSON / PDF

        else Concepto Flow (/concepto)
            Controller->>Controller: ConceptoController
            Controller->>Service: ConceptoService
            Service->>Repository: IConceptoRepository
            Repository->>DB: CRUD
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: Concepto
            Service-->>Controller: Concepto (HATEOAS)
            Controller-->>Client: JSON Response

        else Transaccion Flow (/transaccion)
            Controller->>Controller: TransaccionController
            Controller->>Service: TransaccionService
            Service->>Repository: ITransaccionRepository
            Repository->>DB: CRUD
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: List<Transaccion>
            Service-->>Controller: List<Transaccion>
            Controller-->>Client: JSON Response (HATEOAS)

        else Anotador Flow (/anotador)
            Controller->>Controller: AnotadorController
            Controller->>Service: AnotadorService
            Service->>Repository: IAnotadorRepository
            Repository->>DB: CRUD
            DB-->>Repository: Result
            Repository-->>Service: Anotador
            Service-->>Controller: Anotador (HATEOAS)
            Controller-->>Client: JSON Response

        else Periodo Flow (/periodo)
            Controller->>Controller: PeriodoController
            Controller->>Service: PeriodoService
            Service->>Repository: PeriodoRepository
            Repository->>DB: Consultas
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: Periodo
            Service-->>Controller: Periodo
            Controller-->>Client: JSON Response

        else Combos Flow (/combos)
            Controller->>Controller: CombosController
            Controller->>Service: CombosService
            Service->>Repository: Múltiples Repositories
            Repository->>DB: Consultas de referencia
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: Listas agrupadas
            Service-->>Controller: Map de listas
            Controller-->>Client: JSON (datos para formularios)

        else FacturaParaInteres Flow (/view)
            Controller->>Controller: FacturaParaInteresController
            Controller->>Service: FacturaParaInteresService
            Service->>Repository: IFacturaParaInteresRepository
            Repository->>DB: SELECT with JOIN
            DB-->>Repository: ResultSet
            Repository-->>Service: List<FacturaParaInteres>
            Service-->>Controller: View Model
            Controller-->>Client: JSON Response
        end
    end

    Note over Client,DB: Auditoría: timestamps y usuario registrados por @EnableJpaAuditing
